<i>adverb</i>: 혹여 [호겨], 혹시 [혹씨], 혹 [혹], 어쩌다가 [어쩌다가], 어쩌다 [어쩌다] <i>noun</i>: 돌발적 [돌발쩍] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square"><li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>혹여 [호겨]</dt><br>
<dd>1. by any chance</dd><br>
<dd>그러할 리는 없지만 만약에.</dd><br>
<dd>Not probably but possibly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. accidentally</dd><br>
<dd>어쩌다가 우연히.</dd><br>
<dd>By chance.</dd><br>
<dd>3. maybe</dd><br>
<dd>짐작대로 어쩌면.</dd><br>
<dd>Perhaps as one has guessed.</dd><br>
<dt>혹시 [혹씨]</dt><br>
<dd>1. by any chance</dd><br>
<dd>그러할 리는 없지만 만약에.</dd><br>
<dd>Not probably but possibly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. accidentally</dd><br>
<dd>어쩌다가 우연히.</dd><br>
<dd>By chance.</dd><br>
<dd>3. maybe</dd><br>
<dd>짐작대로 어쩌면.</dd><br>
<dd>Perhaps as one has guessed.</dd><br>
<dd>4. by any chance</dd><br>
<dd>그러리라 생각하지만 분명하지 않아 말하기를 망설일 때 쓰는 말.</dd><br>
<dd>The word that is used when one is hesitant to say something he/she thinks is possible but he/she is uncertain about.</dd><br>
<dt>혹 [혹]</dt><br>
<dd>1. by any chance</dd><br>
<dd>그러할 리는 없지만 만일에.</dd><br>
<dd>Not probably but possibly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. accidentally</dd><br>
<dd>어쩌다가 우연히.</dd><br>
<dd>By chance.</dd><br>
<dd>3. maybe</dd><br>
<dd>짐작대로 어쩌면.</dd><br>
<dd>Perhaps as one has guessed.</dd><br>
<dd>4. sometimes; occasionally; once in a while</dd><br>
<dd>어쩌다가 아주 가끔.</dd><br>
<dd>Sometimes at random intervals.</dd><br>
<dt>어쩌다가 [어쩌다가]</dt><br>
<dd>1. accidentally; by chance</dd><br>
<dd>뜻밖에 우연히.</dd><br>
<dd>Incidentally to one's surprise.</dd><br>
<dd>2. occasionally; now and then</dd><br>
<dd>가끔가다가. 또는 이따금씩.</dd><br>
<dd>Once in a while, or sometimes.</dd><br>
<dt>어쩌다 [어쩌다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. accidentally; by chance</dd><br>
<dd>뜻밖에 우연히.</dd><br>
<dd>Incidentally to one's surprise.</dd><br>
<dd>2. occasionally; now and then</dd><br>
<dd>가끔가다가. 또는 이따금씩.</dd><br>
<dd>Once in a while, or sometimes.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>돌발적 [돌발쩍]</dt><br>
<dd>accidentally; unexpectedly</dd><br>
<dd>예상하지 못한 일이 갑자기 일어나는 것.</dd><br>
<dd>An incident occurring suddenly and unexpectedly.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>